Description: 2016 Paul Reed Smith McCarty 594 10 Top Selling my PRS 594, I purchased this brand new from the famed Willcutt Guitar Shop in late 2017. After purchasing, I got more into playing acoustic full time and this guitar never got played. It is Dead Mint! UNPLAYED Condition. Frets still look like new, action is perfect. I looked at and played several of these before purchasing this one - the wood grain on the top is absolutely striking, what you would expect for a PRS 10 Top. The pictures just don’t do it justice. It is beautiful! This one also has the upgraded color matched maple neck, an absolutely stunning feature!! There is not a mark on the guitar anywhere, no scratches, no dents, no dings, no pick marks, no repairs - it literally looks the same as the day I bought it. It has been in my humidity controlled house since new, no smoke, no pets, no must, no stink. MINT Condition! As much as I want to get back into playing electric, I am unfortunately forced to sell due to financial circumstances. Time to pass it on to a new owner to love and enjoy! Fully insured flat rate shipping to Lower 48 only. PayPal Payment due immediately upon purchase from US based bank account only! Will ship in original case, in original shipping carton as it was when new.
Title: PRS McCarty 594 10 Top, Color Matched Flame Maple Neck - Slate Blue.
